{"tid":2369352,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林柏特盛讚藍軍新星：全能表現！比我22歲時強","createTime":"2021-01-17T05:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T06:48:48.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9e691ab2865bf1eb83ade8c03809c3aa05bbd7","tid":2369352,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"　　車路士1比0擊敗富咸，曼森-蒙特（Mason Mount）攻入唯一入球。賽後，藍軍主教練林柏特（Frank Lampard）盛讚這位22歲新星，稱他比同齡的自己更強。<br />\n<br />\n　　林柏特說：「曼森在比賽中表現傑出，以他的發揮，理應受到讚揚。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「目前曼森的角色稍微有一點後撤，但依然可以進入禁區，他需要攻入更多的入球。他知道這一點，他的能力是非常出色的，他的態度非常棒，因此他配得上這個收穫。我認為他各方面的表現都很棒，去年和今年，他的表現都很好。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當我提到年青人時，他是一個很好的榜樣，上週他滿22歲了，我在22歲時來到車路士，在我第一年裡並沒有讓人驚喜，我當時還在適應，但曼森已經踢了這麼多的比賽了。」"},{"pid":"51cbbc94b5ba9bad7bf1d6cad81842c34f2b339a","tid":2369352,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"新浪三俠又發文"},{"pid":"2a12431ba518467991ca5d2afd65095070907583","tid":2369352,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"22歲算老啦<br />\nGreatwood foden 呢d英人18歲就踢緊班霸"},{"pid":"4b5c6f6ada045eab9716f9e5d45061919c3a1098","tid":2369352,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"有個曼字都係好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8162f797da5e39abf5c2909fbf40b26ce6f45fd5","tid":2369352,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"咁佢又買六子番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a696ea438ea58ce976a9c149b66eab18c5c24f99","tid":2369352,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8162f797da5e39abf5c2909fbf40b26ce6f45fd5","tid":2369352,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"咁佢又買六子番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:06:53.000Z",